### Step D: Android manifest — add inside `<manifest>` before `<application>`
```xml
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SEND_SMS"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_SMS"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC"/>
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.CAMERA"/>
```

Add to `<application>` tag: `android:usesCleartextTraffic="false"`

This enforces HTTPS-only at the OS level. Any accidental plain HTTP call will fail at the network layer, not silently succeed.

### Step E: `android/app/build.gradle`
Set `minSdkVersion 26` in the `defaultConfig` block.

### Step F: `analysis_options.yaml`
```yaml
include: package:flutter_lints/flutter.yaml

linter:
  rules:
    - avoid_print
    - always_declare_return_types
    - prefer_final_locals
    - prefer_const_constructors
    - avoid_dynamic_calls

analyzer:
  errors:
    missing_return: error
    unused_import: error
    dead_code: warning
```

### Step G: Minimal `lib/main.dart`
```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

void main() {
  runApp(const SuperAdminAgentApp());
}

class SuperAdminAgentApp extends StatelessWidget {
  const SuperAdminAgentApp({super.key});

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return MaterialApp(
      title: 'Super Admin Agent',
      debugShowCheckedModeBanner: false,
      home: Scaffold(
        body: Center(
          child: Text(
            'Phase 0: Scaffold Only',
            style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.headlineSmall,
          ),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

---

## 5. Verification — Must ALL Pass Before Phase 1

```bash
# Dependency resolution — must complete with no errors
flutter pub get

# Static analysis — must show "No issues found!"
flutter analyze

# Compilation check — must produce an APK without errors
flutter build apk --debug --no-pub

# Directory existence check — must show all 40+ directories
find lib/ -type d | sort
```

**Do not proceed to Phase 1 if any of these produce errors.**
